data.description: Welcome home! This wonderful 3 bed, 2 bath home has many wonderful features including new roof in 2017 and new gas fireplace insert and new carpet in the living area as of July, 2023. 2010 home remodel included the following: Garage conversion to main bedroom with skylight and ensuite bath including jetted tub, linen cabinet, vanity area and walk in closet. Kitchen update featured new cabinets complete with pull out drawers, turntables, spice storage, pantry and gas stove. Main bath renovation included new vanity, tile accents and walk-in shower.  Vinyl windows throughout including bay window in living room, garden window in dining room and large garden window in hallway. New furnace with forced air gas heat and air conditioning. Underground drainage has been dug under all downspouts, so water company gives % off water bill for no water runoff. Fully fenced back yard features a covered patio, storage building with loft and plenty of room to entertain, BBQ and more. Circle drive ensures that you have plenty of off street parking for all your guests. [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222463]
